                <div class="faq-answer">
                    <p>There's no minimum commitment. Most experts do 2-4 calls per month (about 1-2 hours total). You control your availability and can pause anytime.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="faq-item">
                <button class="faq-question">
                    <h4>What qualifications do I need?</h4>
                    <div class="faq-icon">
                        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                            <polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"/>
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                </button>
                <div class="faq-answer">
                    <p>Real hands-on experience with business software is what matters. You don't need certifications or specific titles—just genuine implementation or daily-use experience you can share authentically.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="faq-item">
                <button class="faq-question">
                    <h4>When and how do I get paid?</h4>
                    <div class="faq-icon">
                        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                            <polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"/>
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                </button>
                <div class="faq-answer">
                    <p>Payment is processed immediately after each completed call. You can receive funds via direct deposit, PayPal, or other supported methods. Rates range from $100-500 per 15-minute conversation.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="faq-item">
                <button class="faq-question">
                    <h4>Can I decline conversation requests?</h4>
                    <div class="faq-icon">
                        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                            <polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"/>
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                </button>
                <div class="faq-answer">
                    <p>Absolutely. You have full control over which conversations to accept. You can also set availability limits and the platform will automatically enforce them.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="faq-item">
                <button class="faq-question">
                    <h4>What will buyers ask me about?</h4>
                    <div class="faq-icon">
                        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                            <polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"/>
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                </button>
                <div class="faq-answer">
                    <p>Buyers typically ask about implementation experiences, day-to-day usage, integrations, challenges you faced, ROI, and honest comparisons with alternatives. Just share your genuine experience.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="faq-item">
